<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="hw29May1938"><font color="red">29 May 1938</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): The missing words (with context) seem to run: &mdash; you&apos;re marchadant too forte so don&apos;t start furlan your ladins till you&apos;ve learned the lie of her landuage! but as I don&apos;t feel entirely sure I am sending herewith the page (15-16, previously 49-50 of <i>transition</i> 26) containing the entire insertion which &hellip; return to me. </div>
